{"tid":2447341,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"John Lennon首imagine算唔算係極致嘅左","createTime":"2021-03-15T06:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T09:13:00.000Z","uid":282619,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"839d7a01555f8060e90c2c6a9b50cc5c323e1d3b","tid":2447341,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又無天堂又無地獄，無宗教，無神論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無國界，無分國家，共產入面嘅不斷革命論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界都有嘢食，共產主義入面嘅經濟分配制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界都係兄弟姊妹，共產入面稱呼嘅同志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有無補充？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055417043c7831238c71c1aae839cca26404e801","tid":2447341,"uid":303274,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"839d7a01555f8060e90c2c6a9b50cc5c323e1d3b","tid":2447341,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又無天堂又無地獄，無宗教，無神論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無國界，無分國家，共產入面嘅不斷革命論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界都有嘢食，共產主義入面嘅經濟分配制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界都係兄弟姊妹，共產入面稱呼嘅同志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有無補充？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:21:27.000Z","msg":"你既唸法係： Lennon=共產<br />\n<br />\n次序係：<br />\n<br />\nLennon唸嘢平等，平等=左，左等於共產，所以Lennon 等於共產。<br />\n<br />\n但左派並唔係only代表共產。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如我信無神論，咁我係咪又係共產？我可以係因為信科學only，又例如我信種族平等亦唔會等於我信左共產主義，可以係科學原因。<br />\n唔可以話兩者之間共通，就話佢係共產主義者。<br />\n<br />\n甚至乎係我覺得，共產主義騎劫左平等呢個概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以先會有咁樣既誤解出現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，你搞錯少少共產主義內容，例如：不斷革命論係講個實行方法，而非「無分國家」呢個理念，又例如Lennon口中既兄弟姐妹係講友善，無歧視相處，唔係一定要有共同目標同信念，但「同志」呢個term係包含埋呢樣嘢。"},{"pid":"a92286f292224afe62e0f1d47ca693d817dc333f","tid":2447341,"uid":362754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:24:37.000Z","msg":"幫樓主補link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://youtu.be/qTfKTKGyJIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqTfKTKGyJIs&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=fb3de9de\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qTfKTKGyJIs</a>"},{"pid":"741f357a3c03ddac29adf86ac6aa1d79e9dbf626","tid":2447341,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:28:38.000Z","msg":"實際都只係 imagine, 首歌既內容係唔會存在"},{"pid":"41fb49519b1dbde94b93af71cb473fa2e205e41a","tid":2447341,"uid":140738,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:45:56.000Z","msg":"佢依個先係真正嘅左<br />\n依家左膠係為左接納人而比好多標籤人<br />\n而John Lennon係話唔要咁多標籤<br />\n即係舉例左膠會分男女 表面男自己認為係女<br />\n表面女而自己認為係男<br />\n但首歌嘅概念就連男女都廢撚事分"},{"pid":"b8b33830109b7815e83c354ea12e88e1482ed975","tid":2447341,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a92286f292224afe62e0f1d47ca693d817dc333f","tid":2447341,"uid":362754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:24:37.000Z","msg":"幫樓主補link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://youtu.be/qTfKTKGyJIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqTfKTKGyJIs&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=fb3de9de\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qTfKTKGyJIs</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:09:58.000Z","msg":"行為藝術？imagine 緊自己彈緊？"},{"pid":"e4a27d1d12bfc7e7927b83f58605affaa1a6dff3","tid":2447341,"uid":300918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8b33830109b7815e83c354ea12e88e1482ed975","tid":2447341,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a92286f292224afe62e0f1d47ca693d817dc333f","tid":2447341,"uid":362754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:24:37.000Z","msg":"幫樓主補link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://youtu.be/qTfKTKGyJIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqTfKTKGyJIs&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=fb3de9de\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qTfKTKGyJIs</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:09:58.000Z","msg":"行為藝術？imagine 緊自己彈緊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:29:31.000Z","msg":"好deep<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8db9745b5771980126cb3c0401f7978c906b09d","tid":2447341,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"055417043c7831238c71c1aae839cca26404e801","tid":2447341,"uid":303274,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"839d7a01555f8060e90c2c6a9b50cc5c323e1d3b","tid":2447341,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又無天堂又無地獄，無宗教，無神論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無國界，無分國家，共產入面嘅不斷革命論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界都有嘢食，共產主義入面嘅經濟分配制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界都係兄弟姊妹，共產入面稱呼嘅同志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br /